{
  "stem": "22979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, when I came back from camp, I could point it out, the houses staring at me, who lived where, and how many children, who was my friend for this family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since, you know, it passed already more than half a century, it's hard to recall that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For First Friday, it must be cleaning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was cleaned, though mainly the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we baked our challah and all of the goodies, the sweets, the breads, at home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, in a small town, usually, you had a special kitchen, where it was also not an oven to bake.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and the smell of those goodies Friday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I always jumped around to want to help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But since, you know, the maid cleaned and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I helped, and I was always wet-- even my hair were wet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we had wooden floors in the kitchen, and everything had to have spic-and-span.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the baking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then in the evening, first of all, my mother lit the candles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was standing on a little chair, because I was never too tall to reach the same way like she did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I helped light the candles, and then my father went to shul.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He came back, we had dinner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the evening, naturally, fish was always there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we had soup and meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, you know, my father made kiddush.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then my brother with him were singing, you know, zemirot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I joined them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my father said, always, shah-- be quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But-- and in the morning-- yeah, and I have to mention.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Friday, also, I had to take a cholent to the baker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because for--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cholent.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For supper-- lunch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I schlepped the big, heavy pot.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
